  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cd592c89ff9faa96.jpg?v=1782532378\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>While creating <a href=\"http://wp.me/p4uKLp-6tF\">this world map wall decal</a> as well as <a href=\"http://wp.me/p4uKLp-6to\">this door sign</a>, I thought I may as well make a little sign for Jack's playroom. I used <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/shop/&amp;aff_id=Mk4NE4JGfCx5y:TOY6$O:A&amp;ad_id=15\">my Silhouette</a> and the <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/june/&amp;aff_id=Mk4NE4JGfCx5y:TOY6$O:A&amp;ad_id=1\">Silhouette Studio</a> software to create a wall decal with white vinyl.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"16b-IMG_3350.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/37749a470bdcaf58.jpg?v=1782532381\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16c-.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/082a3423a5dcc924.jpg?v=1782532384\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16d-IMG_3361.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/78b55b3cf0b3cd3b.jpg?v=1782532387\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16e-IMG_3357.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/37cb1f32e6cb14bf.jpg?v=1782532389\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16f-IMG_3354.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3c916d97df923546.jpg?v=1782532392\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16g-IMG_3364.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4a3f00ed9e8fbee8.jpg?v=1782532395\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16h-IMG_3367.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/13aa43dd2bebc7cd.jpg?v=1782532398\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16i-jack_playroom.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/069df7c74b6f6467.jpg?v=1782532400\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16j-IMG_3379.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/474b3395d45f7d38.jpg?v=1782532403\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Now that I am clearly hooked on creating wall decals, any suggestions on what I should make next?</p>"
